{"tid":249440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網絡紅人Ming仔　指經理人公司毁約後月薪25萬跌至5萬　入稟索償","createTime":"2017-05-19T09:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T10:12:55.000Z","uid":37927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45e5bc3a2198b5f1792ccf4a25505e4097b0a798","tid":249440,"uid":37927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"網絡紅人Ming仔　指經理人公司毁約後月薪25萬跌至5萬　入稟索償<br />\n<br />\n原告梁嘉銘，控告藝員經理人公司Viral Digital Studio Limited毀約，入稟狀指，Ming仔去年8月和公司簽2年合約，公司作為他的專屬經理人，承諾每月支付他25萬元，合約直到2018年8月才完結。<br />\n<br />\n但公司在今年2月通知Ming仔，不會繼續支付薪金和要單方面解約，Ming仔稱公司毀約令他喪失今年2月和3月的薪金共50萬，4月起他變回自由身藝人，月薪跌至每月5萬元，因此向公司追討由今年4月到2018年底的收入損失，合共逾430萬元。<br />\n<br />\n呢間公司係咪有好多藝人GA?"},{"pid":"93d5bb91825f66473621e1d89d607fea282a8869","tid":249440,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"邊撚個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ad7455f63135485da6c3782d6dc0f0b4ccae67","tid":249440,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊撚個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對手係你度，不如試下google<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d658e8ddd74ea718a0bf3dba744bc68a0830e3","tid":249440,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:09:49.000Z","msg":"留名食花生"},{"pid":"4b216cd3ecbc92af8ada36bdf9a99adf535aa58a","tid":249440,"uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:12:55.000Z","msg":"叫得網絡紅人即係唔紅啦<br />\n<br />\n你幾時見周潤發報新聞要叫國際巨星周潤發"}]}